title: Milei camp says first round win is unlikely in Argentina
description:
After shocking Argentinian politics by finishing in first place in the August 13 presidential primaries, libertarian economist Javier Milei’s camp was hoping that momentum could be enough for him to secure a first round win in the October 22 election. But that does not seem to have been the case. With no votes officially counted, […]
